'''Urval'starn''' was a city on the [[Bothan/Legends|Bothan]] [[Homeworld/Legends|homeworld]] of [[Bothawui/Legends|Bothawui]]. 

It was located in the midlands of the [[Planet/Legends|planet's]] western continent. The city [[Gre Shev'starn]] was in the west, and [[Dreel'starn]] to the southeast.

